response.overview: In 1905, revolutionist Sun Yat-Sen visits Hong Kong to discuss plans with Tongmenghui members to overthrow the Qing dynasty. But when they find out that assassins have been sent to kill him, they assemble a group of protectors to prevent any attacks.
response.tagline: To save a nations future, they must protect one man from its past.
response.title: Bodyguards and Assassins
